				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Dialog with harpers in Danthelon's Dancing Axe basement ambush. A number of doppelgangers have slaughered a Harper troop and stolen their faces, forcing the one surviving Harper to set Jaheira up for an ambush.\r\nWe can see the trap coming, or pick up on Jaheira's hint that all is not right. Either way, it ends in combat."
				}
